Seth Sakai https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seth_Sakai 0 Seth Saita Sakai (May 22, 1932 - May 10, 2007) was an American television and film actor. Sakai's roles included various characters from Hawaii Five-O and Magnum, P.I.. He also featured in the 1991 film, The Perfect Weapon.
